Choice of how to use and disclose your information about the turbo lock. Swagtron strives to provide you with choices about the personal information you provide us. The turbine lock has created a mechanism to provide you with the following information controls:

· Track technology and advertising. You can set your browser to reject all or part of your browser Cookie, or to alert you when Cookie are sent. To learn how to manage Flash cookie settings, visit the Flash Player settings page on the Adobe website. If you disable or reject cookie, please note that some parts of this website may not be accessible or operate normally.

· Disclose your information for third-party advertising. We will not share your personal information with non associated or non agent third parties for promotional purposes.

· Swagtron Promotions。 If you do not want Swagtron to use your email address to promote our own or third-party products or services, you can opt out by clicking the "Unsubscribe" link in any of these email footers. If we send you a promotional email, you can send us a reply email and ask to omit it in future email distribution.

· Targeted advertising。 If you do not want us to use the information we collect or the information you provide us to advertise according to the advertisers' target audience preferences, you can opt out according to the instructions on the following link:http://www.criteo.com/deactivate-criteo-banners/

· 

Swagtron does not control the collection or use of your information by third parties to provide interest based advertising. However, these third parties may provide you with a way to choose not to collect or use your information in this way. You can choose not to receive targeted ads ("Nai") from members of the Internet Advertising Promotion Association on NAI's website.

Your California privacy.  Section 1798.83 of the California Civil Code allows California resident users of our website to request certain information about our disclosure of personal information to third parties for their direct marketing purposes. To make such a request, please email support@swagtron.com Or write to us: Swagtron, 3431 William Richardson Dr., Ste B, South bond, Indiana 46628.

Data security. Unfortunately, transmitting information over the Internet is not completely secure. Although we do our best to protect your personal information, we cannot guarantee the security of your personal information transferred to our website. Any transmission of personal information is at your own risk. Swagtron is not responsible for circumventing any privacy settings or security measures contained in this website.

 

Change our privacy policy.  It is our policy to post any changes to our privacy policy on this page. If we make major changes to the way we handle users' personal information, we will notify you through the notice on the website home page. The last revision date of the privacy policy is identified at the top of the page. You are responsible for ensuring that we provide you with the latest valid and deliverable email address, and regularly visit our website and this privacy policy to check for any changes.

 

Can Spam Act. The CAN-SPAM Act is a law that sets rules for commercial e-mail, stipulates requirements for commercial e-mail, grants recipients the right to stop sending e-mail to them, and provides severe penalties for violations. We collect your email address to send information, respond to queries and/or other requests or questions. In order to comply with CANSPAM, we agree to the following:

· Do not use false or misleading subjects or email addresses.

· Identify messages as advertisements in a reasonable way.

·Include the actual address of our business or site headquarters.

· Monitor the compliance of third-party email marketing services, if used.

· Express cashout opt out/unsubscribe requests.

· Allow users to unsubscribe using the link at the bottom of each email.

· If you want to unsubscribe from future emails at any time, you can unsubscribe according to the instructions at the bottom of each email, and we will immediately delete you from all future communications.

